    "description": "<strong>Story Mode: </strong>Reclaim Your Soul Shards, Conquer the Trails, Battle Bosses, Track Your Score and Grow In Power to Complete the Story. <br><strong>Rift Mode: </strong>Survive Is Key, Increase Your Score, Gain Powerful Items and Defeat Auto Generated Mobs In a Race Against Time.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Void: Edge of Existence<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2> <strong>- Reclaim Your Soul in a Single Player RPG</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246390/extras/d65df4174ef6425f1ebe5e8993b42809.poster.avif?t=1690741930\" width=630 height=122 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246390/extras/d65df4174ef6425f1ebe5e8993b42809.webm?t=1690741930\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246390/extras/d65df4174ef6425f1ebe5e8993b42809.mp4?t=1690741930\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Take part in an epic adventure as Andral, a Sentinel of Arronia, who was betrayed and lost his soul. Undertake trials to reclaim it and seek retribution in the realm of Xeross.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246390/extras/d273dc90001b25141e9721125db542a6.poster.avif?t=1690741930\" width=630 height=122 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246390/extras/d273dc90001b25141e9721125db542a6.webm?t=1690741930\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features:</h2>Follow Andral's journey through the trials of reforging his soul and seeking retribution from his betrayer.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246390/extras/40bb38463bcdc129f0ea7cdc612c5564.poster.avif?t=1690741930\" width=630 height=122 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246390/extras/40bb38463bcdc129f0ea7cdc612c5564.webm?t=1690741930\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246390/extras/40bb38463bcdc129f0ea7cdc612c5564.mp4?t=1690741930\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Level scaling progression:</h2>The game scales bosses and mobs based on the level state, which increases with every completion of the game.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246390/extras/0530f41bc6ee90c80290996a481d578d.poster.avif?t=1690741930\" width=630 height=122 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246390/extras/0530f41bc6ee90c80290996a481d578d.webm?t=1690741930\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >In-game collections and hidden items:</h2>Discover unique items that can adjust your base stats or affect gameplay, obtained through defeating bosses or secret combinations.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246390/extras/f4e82f72e4707779f37ec1327c6cde0c.poster.avif?t=1690741930\" width=630 height=122 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246390/extras/f4e82f72e4707779f37ec1327c6cde0c.webm?t=1690741930\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246390/extras/f4e82f72e4707779f37ec1327c6cde0c.mp4?t=1690741930\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Player-controlled skill power</h2>Adapt your character's base, higher, and ability stats before each trial, increasing skill power with soul fragments or soul shards.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246390/extras/422bf0dab6b458db7787ec35f2cb765d.poster.avif?t=1690741930\" width=630 height=122 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246390/extras/422bf0dab6b458db7787ec35f2cb765d.webm?t=1690741930\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246390/extras/422bf0dab6b458db7787ec35f2cb765d.mp4?t=1690741930\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Void: Edge of Existence</strong> is a single player trial-based RPG where you undertake trials to reclaim your soul and seek retribution from your betrayer. With each completion of the game, the level state increases, scaling bosses and mobs and unlocking items after a certain level has been achieved. Discover hidden items with unique effects that can adjust your base stats or affect gameplay, obtained through defeating bosses or secret combinations. You have full control of your skill power, which can be traded with soul fragments or soul shards to increase your base, higher, and ability stats before each trial.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246390/extras/6b845d88e9210d5aa101608d2abd9a56.poster.avif?t=1690741930\" width=630 height=122 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246390/extras/6b845d88e9210d5aa101608d2abd9a56.webm?t=1690741930\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246390/extras/6b845d88e9210d5aa101608d2abd9a56.mp4?t=1690741930\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>If you like narrative-driven RPGs, level scaling progression, hidden items, and player-controlled skill power, then Void: Edge of Existence is the game for you. Reclaim your soul and seek retribution in this epic adventure of Andral.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246390/extras/2439e59c34c638b1ed507f918373f3ae.avif?t=1690741930\" width=318 height=198 /></span><br></h2>",
